{"tid":2423543,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界根本冇人重視我","createTime":"2021-02-26T03:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T16:11:51.000Z","uid":251510,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"48a836348d33f26ba093d3a1efd6b8d6bff9b9eb","tid":2423543,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"好想死，但又冇勇氣死"},{"pid":"01ff874cefe7ac7815311faa4ed008b96487e8ef","tid":2423543,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:24:50.000Z","msg":"連屋企人都對我唔上心"},{"pid":"0e669392e9d20e82b4ce4a0cb612cabb6f65d9aa","tid":2423543,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:25:45.000Z","msg":"我同透明根本冇分別<br />\n我死咗，都唔會有人想去我嘅葬禮"},{"pid":"d6aeb7139c1aff637600c7d1c3d6b95cab29ece7","tid":2423543,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"一係唔重視我<br />\n一係關注我，想睇我仆街<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，冇第三種人"},{"pid":"eccbe7f9b9a6211e5b62ca72ecaf5f3835c4f12a","tid":2423543,"uid":200529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:32:24.000Z","msg":"你重視自己就得"},{"pid":"26380096742d69591b1c9bb95b0252e26dd22db0","tid":2423543,"uid":221093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"你啲朋友呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2443ea18b4fd17f07327eacb1522bcf1fdcab71a","tid":2423543,"uid":288437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"第三種人重視你 但係你唔重視佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310a64976611968e8e9db90cff82bb9d593a8cb0","tid":2423543,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3beeb3eac0e15d54b8ead5b3e47cdd438ef3bb82","tid":2423543,"uid":62025,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"唔理你係咪假膠,純粹想分享下可能有其他人都會睇到<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">建議增值自己</span><br />\n例如最簡單係去做gym, 如果覺得太貴/負擔唔到, 可以上youtube search 下有好多gym/fitness片教你簡單/徙手健身<br />\n做運動真係可以改善到生理+心理健康<br />\n另外都可以學下新嘢/搵下新興趣, eg上面講過gym, 增進下文書技能(如果啱用), 語言之類<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己都係過來人,喺frd入面永遠唔會係重要果個,亦都唔係人地既最親<br />\n但過咗一排就睇化咗,重點唔係人地重唔重視你,而係自己重唔重視自己<br />\n如果你唔重視自己既時候,人地根本冇必要重視你<br />\n但你有價值而重視自己多過人地既睇法既時候,自然會有人重視你<br />\n加油,第一步永遠係最難,當你成功做到第一步,自然有第二第三步永遠落去<br />\n唔好咁重視其他人既目光,盡量唔好同人比較(我知唔係咁易)<br />\n應該同自己比較, 今日既我係咪勁過三個月之前既我? 所有嘢都有累積得番黎"},{"pid":"f126d8a5dfc15b4c1cc87cfdb33186c11c75fed9","tid":2423543,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310a64976611968e8e9db90cff82bb9d593a8cb0","tid":2423543,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:28:47.000Z","msg":"屌你殺咗我啦，我冇勇氣"},{"pid":"15b2860e13082f248c1ac807cb6c2676b1bfeacf","tid":2423543,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2443ea18b4fd17f07327eacb1522bcf1fdcab71a","tid":2423543,"uid":288437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"第三種人重視你 但係你唔重視佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"404 error"},{"pid":"961acbcb007c96f58e53d24544df8fefe1118982","tid":2423543,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f126d8a5dfc15b4c1cc87cfdb33186c11c75fed9","tid":2423543,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310a64976611968e8e9db90cff82bb9d593a8cb0","tid":2423543,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-0